eclipse writhing

step 1 - python install - https://www.python.org/

step 2 - eclipse install - https://eclipse.org/

step 3 - PyDev plug-in install
	eclipse menu - Help > Install New Software... >
	add Work with >
		Name : PyDev
		Location : http://pydev.org/updates
	PyDev checked >
	run > run > auto restart eclipse
step 4 - interpreter setting
	eclipse menu - Windows > Preferences
		left tab - PyDev > Interpeters > Python Interpreter
		Quick Auto-Config button Click > OK button click
step 5 - system environmental variable setting
	path - python install location setting
step 6 - pip install - version 2.9 ~ auto install
	system environmental variable setting
	path - python install location forder/Scripts
step 7 - console test
	console - pip, python, python exit > exit()

